Q:2) Write a script to keep track of number of times the web page has been 
accessed. 
 :-----------------------------
<?php
//session start
session_start();
if(isset($_SESSION['count']))
{
$_SESSION['count'] = $_SESSION['count'] +1;
}
else
{
$_SESSION['count'] =1;
}
echo " No of times the web page has been access ".$_SESSION['count'];
?>

